= Installation =
'''1. Launch Dom0 Terminal'''

In Dom0 -> Application Launcher Menu -> System Tools:

* Click on the "Konsole (Terminal)" app to launch it.

'''2. Install Whonix-Gateway and Whonix-Workstation TemplateVM'''

In Dom0 -> Terminal:

* Input command: <code>sudo qubes-dom0-update --enablerepo=qubes-templates-community qubes-template-whonix-gw qubes-template-whonix-ws</code>

'''3. Enable AppArmor''' '''(Optional security enhancement. Currently testers-only.)''' 

whonix-gw:

{{
Qubes_AppArmor
|vmname=whonix-gw
}}

whonix-ws:

{{
